  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine what can activate brown adipose tissue (BAT).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      We will investigate different stimuli (i.e. hormones) to determine which can stimulate BAT.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
